\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16212999 WB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8347148\charrsid6645626 That's right, the chap - the regular chapel}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15802168\charrsid6645626 -}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8347148\charrsid6645626 goers.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8137580 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8347148\charrsid6645626 You said something about school and Sunday school, were you referring then to teachers and Sunday school superintend}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
