\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16212999 WB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8347148\charrsid6645626 That's right. That's right.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8137580 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8347148\charrsid6645626 So they were respected as well?
