\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16212999 WB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8347148\charrsid6645626 Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8137580 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8347148\charrsid6645626 Did you come into contact with them quite a lot, the teachers and Sunday school Superintend}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid15802168\charrsid6645626 e}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8347148\charrsid6645626 nts?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16212999 WB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8347148\charrsid6645626 Well - anybody wanted anything they all seemed to come to our house - for me dad and - and he said, well our Billy'll go and do it.
