\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16212999 WB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8347148\charrsid6645626 Oh yes, we'd farmers, we'd - we'd - we'd local farmers all - all round us, little farms you know.
