\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8137580 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8347148\charrsid6645626 This was Prince Smith and Ste}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14437611\charrsid6645626 l}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid8347148\charrsid6645626 l?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16212999 WB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8347148\charrsid6645626 That - this - the - the - the - engineering where they built the machine yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8137580 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8347148\charrsid6645626 Did you get any holidays with pay when you were }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14437611\charrsid6645626 
working at Prince Smith and Stel}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8347148\charrsid6645626 l?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16212999 WB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8347148\charrsid6645626 Neve}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14437611\charrsid6645626 r}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8347148\charrsid6645626 
- only in - when - these later years I mean.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8137580 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8347148\charrsid6645626 Not then?
