t back in the services, and I were - I were in - in India for seven year. But - in that firm I worked for, if - if - if you were soldiering, your service counted. Well, and then I worked through until I got the - a pretty good job, I used to do all the lu
bricating in the works, and then when the last war started - they asked for - under Lord Belisha scheme for ex-NOO's}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14437611\charrsid6645626  to train mi}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8347148\charrsid6645626 
