\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16212999 WB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8347148\charrsid6645626 That's right.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8137580 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8347148\charrsid6645626 As a fitter?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16212999 WB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8347148\charrsid6645626 That's right.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8137580 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8347148\charrsid6645626 Do you think you would be preferred another type of occupation?
