\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16212999 WB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8347148\charrsid6645626 No, because - you see, I - the - the job I - I - I were doing - in entailed me - I - I - I had to work while quarter t
o eight every night. Because - when I'd finished me own job at half past five I'd twenty-three cleaners, office cleaners, women - had to see to all them. And - by the time I got home - I were ready to sit down never mind -
